reviews.review_text: Best Sourse I have heard Best Sourse I have heard, I have a master patched out of the boomie Sennheisers and this is much clearer, more present. One of my favorite Bertha’s, the “Test Me Test Me” line just explodes. I remember looking up and thinking wow, this is going to be a fun night.
